CI/CD Pipeline Setup - Step by Step Guide

1. Create Git Repository & Files

Step 1: Create Repository
- Go to GitHub → Click New Repository
- Repository Name: docker_proj
- Visibility: Public
- Click Create Repository

Step 2: Create Files

index.html:
